snippet: Biles of the United States capped her dominance at the world championships by winning gold medals on the balance beam and the floor exercise on the final day of competition in Nanning, China.
abstract: American gymnast Simone Biles wins gold medals on balance beam and floor exercise on final day of competition in Nanning, China.
lead_paragraph: Biles of the United States capped her dominance at the world championships by winning gold medals on the balance beam and the floor exercise on the final day of competition in Nanning, China.

headline.main: Two More Golds for Simone Biles
